        <odd id="ref3">
            <head>General note</head>
            <p>Compare this address with Bell's "Aerial Locomotion," National Geographic Magazine 18(Jan. 1907):1-34, with 33 illustrations.</p>
        </odd>
        <bioghist id="ref6">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Inventor Alexander Graham Bell became a member of the American Philsophical Society in 1882.</p>
